item.title: Prayer bpn10181 in Māori
item.description: *KIA KOTAHI TE TĀKINA I ROTO I TE RUA TEKAU *MĀ WHĀ HAORA, I TE RĀNUI Tēnei ahau te whakaatu nei, E tōku Atua, Nāu ahau i hanga kia mōhio ahau ki a Koe, kia koropiko hoki ki a Koe. Ko tāku i tēnei wā he whakaatu i tōku kahakore, ināhoki ki Tōu kaha rawa, ki tōku rawakore, ā, ki Tōu whairawa. Kāore kau he Atua i tua atu i a Koe, te Pouāwhinai ngā Wā Mōrearea, te Matua-kore
